These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, sprite
3 different games are played: chess, monopoly, scrabble
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, bolivar, blend
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, rabbit, turtle
The people have 3 different jobs:  scientist, social-worker, writer
There are 3 different favourite colors: yellow, grey, blue
 1. the person who likes blue is the bolivar-smoker##1
 2. the writer is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 3. the havana-smoker is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 4. the person who likes blue is on the far right##1
 5. the bolivar-smoker is the person playing chess##1
 6. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is the person drinking sprite##1
 8. the person playing monopoly is in the middle##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
10. the scientist is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2       |    3     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | sprite        | lemonade |
| Game          | scrabble    | monopoly        | chess    |
| Cigar   | blend        | havana        | bolivar    |
| Pet           | turtle        | chinchilla    | rabbit   |
| Job         | social-worker    | writer | scientist |
| Color     | grey     | yellow          | blue     |

