.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-1-2::.
3 different games are played: scrabble, whist, snooker
The people have 3 different jobs:  electrician, paramedic, software-developer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, satire, zombie
City: liverpool, edinburgh, hannover
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, frog, fish
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, lemonade
1. the electrician is the person traveling to hannover##1
2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
3. the electrician is on the left of the software-developer##1
4. the owner of the frog is on the far left##1
5. the person playing scrabble is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
6. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
7. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
8. the electrician is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
9. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |         3          |
| Game         | snooker    | scrabble     | whist            |
| Job           | paramedic | electrician | software-developer |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | satire      | zombie             |
| City   | liverpool | hannover     | edinburgh             |
| Pet         | frog  | fish       | guinea-pig           |
| Beverage     | lemonade     | hot-chocolate   | almond-milk            |

