.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-1-3::.
House: townhouse, art-deco, colonial
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, photographer, videographer
City: edinburgh, liverpool, colone
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, badminton, cycling
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, reggae, jazz
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, quad-bike, train
1. the art-deco house is on the right of the dressmaker##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left##1
3. the fan of reggae is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
4. the fan of house is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
5. the person driving the train is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
6. the fan of jazz is the person driving the bus##1
7. the fan of house is the person traveling to liverpool##1
8. the townhouse house is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
9. the person who's sport is badminton is the videographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3       |
| House         | colonial  | townhouse     | art-deco    |
| Job           | photographer | dressmaker  | videographer |
| City   | colone       | edinburgh | liverpool      |
| Sport   | cricket     | cycling      | badminton     |
| Music-Genre           | jazz          | reggae      | house   |
| Transport     | bus          | train       | quad-bike    |

