City: boston, edinburgh, new-york
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, purple, pink
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, parkour, weightlifting
 1. the person playing canasta is on the right of the nurse##1
 2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 3. the photographer is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
 4. the person traveling to boston is the fisherman##1
 5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 7. the fisherman is on the far left##1
 8. the person eating lime is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
 9. the person eating mango is on the far right##1
10. the person traveling to new-york is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3       |
| Game      | whist | chess      | canasta        |
| Food          | strawberry  | lime        | mango         |
| Job         | fisherman     | nurse | photographer  |
