.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: apricot, corn, mango
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, hot-chocolate, mirinda
The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, manager, analyst
3 different games are played: backgammon, go, bridge
3 different pets are kept: bird, cat, mouse
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, white, lilac
1. the manager is in the middle##1
2. the person who likes lilac is the person eating corn##1
3. the person eating mango is on the left of the analyst##1
4. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing go##1
5. the person who likes white is the person drinking tea##1
6. the owner of the mouse is in the middle##1
7. the person drinking mirinda is the owner of the cat##1
8. the person playing backgammon is on the far left##1
9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |      3       |
| Food          | corn          | mango      | apricot      |
| Beverage         | mirinda        | hot-chocolate | tea      |
| Job   | musician          | manager        | analyst       |
| Game   | backgammon       | go   | bridge      |
| Pet           | cat           | mouse      | bird         |
| Color         | lilac | red    | white |

 